# 🚀 Day 13 – Lists (One of the Most Important Python Topics)

Welcome to **Day 13!** 🎉

Today is one of the biggest milestones in your Python journey.

Up until now, you've been storing **one value** in one variable.

Example:

```python
patient_name = "Srujan"
```

But what if your hospital has **100 patients?**

Are you going to write:

```python
patient1 = "Srujan"
patient2 = "Gayatri"
patient3 = "Ishanvi"
patient4 = "Madhavi"
...
```

Of course not.

That's why Python has **Lists**.

